Recommends: nginx,
Description: Lua scripting module for Nginx stream (TCP/UDP) subsystem
 Embeds LuaJIT into the Nginx stream subsystem, enabling Lua scripting
 for TCP and UDP proxying. Provides directives such as
 content_by_lua_block, balancer_by_lua_file, init_worker_by_lua_block,
 log_by_lua_block, and preread_by_lua_block in stream server contexts.
 .
 Also supports lua_shared_dict for shared memory zones, cosocket API
 for non-blocking TCP/UDP communication, and SSL certificate handling
 via ssl_certificate_by_lua_block.
